WEBVTT

00:00:20.634 --> 00:00:23.386
(Lin Qianqian, Zhu Helai's Daughter)

00:00:32.570 --> 00:00:34.060
(Xiangyun Hotel, Beiyan County, 1993)

00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:35.560
I wonder if you like the food today.

00:00:35.719 --> 00:00:36.500
Sure, Mr. Huang.

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.799
That's good.

00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:39.939
- Thanks, Mr. Huang. Bye.
- Okay.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.039
Bye. See you.

00:00:41.659 --> 00:00:42.420
Bye, Mr. Huang.

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:43.340
Alright. Bye.

00:00:56.060 --> 00:00:56.740
Who are you?

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:00.560
Mr. Huang, can we talk?

00:01:01.560 --> 00:01:03.060
I don't know you. What's to talk?

00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:04.519
Help!

00:01:15.799 --> 00:01:16.780
Let's talk this out.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:18.700
Don't yell. We have a few questions.

00:01:20.340 --> 00:01:22.400
I won't yell.
Dude, get your hands off me.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:24.200
You... You...

00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:25.540
Get off. Get off now.

00:01:26.700 --> 00:01:27.340
Don't yell.

00:01:27.340 --> 00:01:28.000
Okay, I won't.

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:36.000
Who do you think
you're scaring with a chisel?

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:36.840
Keep it down.

00:01:37.180 --> 00:01:37.780
Behave.

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:40.420
Wait, who are you?
I don't know you people.

00:01:40.420 --> 00:01:41.280
Keep it down.

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.540
Beiyan's Firecracker Man.

00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:46.760
- Who?
- Guangcai.

00:01:46.760 --> 00:01:48.680
Ever heard of Beiyan's Firecracker Man?

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:56.920
Guangcai, the guy who hung firecrackers?

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:59.620
- Glad to see you.
- Enough with the chit-chat.

00:01:59.620 --> 00:02:02.120
Tell us, when will you pay back?

00:02:03.620 --> 00:02:04.540
Well, I...

00:02:06.219 --> 00:02:07.120
Wait.

00:02:08.060 --> 00:02:09.139
I don't owe you money.

00:02:09.139 --> 00:02:09.840
Stop yelling.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:10.939
Pay back whoever you owe.

00:02:11.139 --> 00:02:12.360
I might kill you.

00:02:13.219 --> 00:02:14.919
Kill me? Go ahead.
Smash it here. Smash it.

00:02:14.919 --> 00:02:16.800
Smash it! Smash it!

00:02:22.740 --> 00:02:25.020
Guys, calm down.

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:26.699
Listen to me.

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:29.740
I really don't have the money right now.

00:02:29.860 --> 00:02:30.800
To be honest with you,

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:32.900
my money is tied up with someone else.

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:35.960
How about this?
Once I get it back, I'll pay. Okay?

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:38.300
You have money to eat out
but not to pay up?

00:02:38.860 --> 00:02:39.580
You don't get it.

00:02:39.900 --> 00:02:41.860
I spent the little money
to make big money.

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:43.699
You think I enjoy drinking every day?

00:02:43.699 --> 00:02:44.639
Mr. Huang, listen.

00:02:44.860 --> 00:02:46.680
I know you have your difficulties too.

00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:48.800
You don't owe us money.

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:52.080
But you owe money to those
working on your construction site.

00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:55.740
They need that money
to feed their families.

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:58.240
Today, if you don't
clear up the money issue

00:02:58.460 --> 00:02:59.740
and pay up, you're not leaving.

00:02:59.740 --> 00:03:00.860
Forget about leaving.

00:03:00.860 --> 00:03:02.400
Alright, dude. Listen to me.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.020
Right now,
I really don't have the money.

00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:07.120
I've heard about what you do.

00:03:07.620 --> 00:03:09.300
You've collected
a lot of money for others.

00:03:09.300 --> 00:03:11.520
Hearing about your actions moves me.

00:03:12.020 --> 00:03:15.400
But I'm telling you,
I really don't have the money.

00:03:16.580 --> 00:03:17.419
How about this?

00:03:17.419 --> 00:03:19.580
Give me three days.

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:21.020
Just three days.

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:23.080
Once I get the money back, I'll pay.

00:03:23.300 --> 00:03:25.300
Stop the nonsense. You're just stalling.

00:03:25.300 --> 00:03:26.020
Aren't you?

00:03:26.020 --> 00:03:28.400
No. What would I be stalling for?

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:31.000
To be honest, I built this building.

00:03:31.699 --> 00:03:33.740
I can run away,
but this building won't disappear.

00:03:34.580 --> 00:03:35.520
Don't believe me?

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:36.740
How about this?

00:03:38.419 --> 00:03:39.500
This is my room key.

00:03:39.639 --> 00:03:41.240
Go to my room and stay for three days.

00:03:41.500 --> 00:03:44.020
Eat and drink as you want.
It's all on me. Deal?

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:44.919
Three days.

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:50.300
Three days it is.

00:03:50.460 --> 00:03:51.300
Just three days.

00:05:01.221 --> 00:05:04.378
=The Silent Rift=

00:05:04.378 --> 00:05:07.194
=Episode 4=
(Six Hundred Thousand)

00:05:07.420 --> 00:05:08.800
Let me in to take a look.

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:22.480
Guangcai, the floor is soft.

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:23.920
Guangcai!

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:29.180
Guangcai, the sofa is soft too.

00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:31.800
Feels like I'm sinking right into it.

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:35.480
S-Such a big bed?

00:05:40.180 --> 00:05:42.300
Guangcai, look.

00:05:43.740 --> 00:05:44.480
Look.

00:05:44.860 --> 00:05:45.860
A swimming pool.

00:05:45.860 --> 00:05:48.560
Guangcai, what's this room for?

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:51.100
There's also a phone. And this thing.

00:05:51.100 --> 00:05:52.360
It's a toilet, I guess.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:52.980
Guangcai.

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:55.680
Look. An oil painting.

00:05:56.740 --> 00:06:00.240
Ocean with sailboats. So pretty.

00:06:01.100 --> 00:06:02.420
These are all your favorites.

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:03.560
It's painted so well.

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:09.180
Guangcai, look.
There's so much food here.

00:06:10.879 --> 00:06:12.300
This is good.

00:06:13.300 --> 00:06:16.980
Mr. Huang said
we can eat and stay here as we want.

00:06:16.980 --> 00:06:18.480
Then let's not hold back.

00:06:19.060 --> 00:06:21.180
We'll live it up for a few days.

00:06:55.740 --> 00:06:59.920
Guangcai, is this
the highest spot in Beiyan?

00:07:00.620 --> 00:07:04.480
Look at those people down below,
as tiny as ants.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:10.120
Over there.
That's our construction site.

00:07:10.500 --> 00:07:12.040
Look. Right... right there.

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:22.360
Guangcai, if I ever get rich,

00:07:22.620 --> 00:07:25.800
I'll live here every day
and eat all this stuff.

00:07:26.300 --> 00:07:27.680
Eating here every day?

00:07:32.540 --> 00:07:36.180
What about you, Lijun?
If you're rich, what will you do?

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:38.300
If I get rich,

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:40.800
I'll take someone I like

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:43.180
to sail out to sea.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:48.060
Be it as a captain or a crew member.

00:07:48.060 --> 00:07:50.120
I'll be free and unfettered with her,

00:07:51.060 --> 00:07:52.060
just drifting.

00:07:55.740 --> 00:07:59.040
Drifting at sea every day?
Aren't you afraid you'd get seasick?

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:01.740
I've got a ship. What's there to fear?
I'm the captain.

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:17.800
Imagine if we hadn't come up here today,

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:19.980
we might never

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:23.240
have seen a view like this
our whole lives.

00:08:24.620 --> 00:08:25.980
Look at the streets.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.500
Not a single wheel

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:30.420
down there is ours.

00:08:37.539 --> 00:08:40.480
And in those buildings,
not a single light

00:08:41.799 --> 00:08:42.679
is ours.

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:48.659
But isn't this the city?

00:08:48.659 --> 00:08:50.960
The city belongs to the city folk.

00:08:52.100 --> 00:08:53.080
City folk?

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:56.080
Why can't we become city folk?

00:08:57.740 --> 00:08:59.200
Aren't we standing here right now?

00:09:00.500 --> 00:09:01.860
We're staying here today,

00:09:02.740 --> 00:09:04.399
but that's what someone else owes us.

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:07.200
Someday,

00:09:08.159 --> 00:09:10.279
we'll earn our place here on our own.

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:15.740
Guangcai,

00:09:16.779 --> 00:09:19.279
from now on,
Lijun and I will follow you.

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:21.200
Whatever you tell us to do, we'll do it.

00:09:26.460 --> 00:09:27.500
Someday,

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:30.720
we'll stand in an even taller building

00:09:31.340 --> 00:09:32.259
as bosses.

00:09:34.139 --> 00:09:35.519
Everything we're dreaming of now

00:09:37.019 --> 00:09:38.480
will become real.

00:09:39.100 --> 00:09:41.139
I want to live here forever.

00:09:41.139 --> 00:09:43.460
From now on, I'm staying here.

00:09:43.460 --> 00:09:46.720
I want to sail far away.

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:50.460
I want to live here.

00:09:54.860 --> 00:09:55.840
Your surname, sir?

00:09:56.879 --> 00:10:00.399
Mr. Wang, we'll reserve
a private room for you tonight.

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:01.139
No.

00:10:01.139 --> 00:10:01.720
Okay.

00:10:01.899 --> 00:10:04.879
Just ask who just called.

00:10:05.779 --> 00:10:06.620
I did.

00:10:06.620 --> 00:10:08.980
You called us, right?

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:11.899
Yes, you're the guests
in room 6123, correct?

00:10:11.899 --> 00:10:12.639
Yes.

00:10:13.100 --> 00:10:14.220
Here's the thing, sir.

00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:16.639
Your previous deposit is almost used up.

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:18.899
And your recent expenses have been high.

00:10:20.039 --> 00:10:21.940
Could you provide an additional deposit?

00:10:21.940 --> 00:10:23.379
What room fee?

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:27.100
When we checked in that day,
it was Mr. Huang, remember?

00:10:27.100 --> 00:10:28.279
He got the room for us.

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:30.960
He said he'd cover all the expenses.

00:10:31.460 --> 00:10:32.720
Who is Mr. Huang?

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:33.879
He's your boss.

00:10:33.879 --> 00:10:35.139
He said he'd pay for us.

00:10:35.259 --> 00:10:36.139
The bald guy.

00:10:36.399 --> 00:10:38.779
I'm sorry,
but he's just an ordinary guest here.

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:41.139
He only paid a deposit to get a room.

00:10:41.639 --> 00:10:44.860
As for the rest, please pay up soon.

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:45.860
Wait.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:48.139
He offered us a free stay
while we wait for him.

00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:49.879
You call him and ask him.

00:10:50.899 --> 00:10:52.500
I... I can't reach him.

00:10:53.019 --> 00:10:54.980
You can't reach him?

00:10:54.980 --> 00:10:56.460
Well, we can't reach him, either.

00:10:57.100 --> 00:10:59.340
The matters between you
are not my concern.

00:10:59.340 --> 00:11:01.860
But I do know your outstanding bill
must be settled.

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:05.580
Settle what? What outstanding bill?

00:11:05.740 --> 00:11:08.000
Wasn't it you who ate
all the abalones and lobsters?

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:08.620
Wait.

00:11:09.620 --> 00:11:10.879
Miss, how much is it roughly?

00:11:11.620 --> 00:11:12.899
It's

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:14.840
2,558 yuan in total.

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:17.840
What? Over 2,000?

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:19.759
Here's the receipt. See for yourself.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:22.019
Well...

00:11:23.139 --> 00:11:24.100
You ask him.

00:11:24.100 --> 00:11:25.139
- Call him.
- Yes, call him.

00:11:25.139 --> 00:11:26.460
He was supposed to pay for this.

00:11:26.460 --> 00:11:27.460
We're not handling this.

00:11:27.460 --> 00:11:29.620
Just get him to pay.

00:11:29.620 --> 00:11:31.220
Security, stop them.

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:32.600
Call the police.

00:11:32.600 --> 00:11:35.340
You stayed, ordered food,
and now want to skip the bill?

00:11:40.399 --> 00:11:41.620
Zhu is here.

00:11:42.519 --> 00:11:43.120
Zhu.

00:11:46.340 --> 00:11:47.460
Let me see the bill.

00:11:47.460 --> 00:11:47.980
Okay.

00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:54.700
2,558 yuan?

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:56.639
Is it right?

00:11:56.840 --> 00:11:59.480
Zhu, we've checked. The number is right.

00:11:59.480 --> 00:12:01.000
But Mr. Huang should be paying it.

00:12:01.379 --> 00:12:03.100
Exactly, it's that scammer's fault.

00:12:03.100 --> 00:12:05.340
I told you to demand payment
from that scammer.

00:12:05.340 --> 00:12:06.360
Don't be unreasonable.

00:12:07.399 --> 00:12:09.080
Miss, on the phone just now,

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:11.480
they've explained the whole story to me.

00:12:11.720 --> 00:12:12.600
I can testify to that.

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:15.600
Look, they definitely
can't pay this amount right now.

00:12:15.860 --> 00:12:18.360
Officer, aren't you
making things difficult for us?

00:12:18.580 --> 00:12:20.519
As you can see,
we're a legitimate business.

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:22.019
We can't waive this payment.

00:12:23.580 --> 00:12:24.200
How about this?

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.840
(Police Badge)
Here's my badge. I'll vouch for them.

00:12:29.620 --> 00:12:30.720
Let them write an IOU.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:33.220
They can't pay nothing at all, right?

00:12:33.399 --> 00:12:35.379
I can't explain it to my superiors.

00:12:36.340 --> 00:12:38.600
Zhu, how about this?

00:12:39.519 --> 00:12:41.139
I'll stay here as collateral, okay?

00:12:41.460 --> 00:12:43.879
And Lijun and Dazhu
will find that Huang guy.

00:12:43.879 --> 00:12:45.879
Guangcai, keep it down.

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:52.019
Here's my paycheck from today
as partial payment.

00:12:52.460 --> 00:12:54.620
They can pay the rest gradually.

00:12:54.620 --> 00:12:55.639
I'll write the guarantee.

00:12:56.720 --> 00:12:59.460
See what trouble
you've caused the officer?

00:13:02.490 --> 00:13:06.234
(Guarantee Letter)

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:20.100
How many times have I told you?
Stay out of debt collection.

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:24.139
You never listen when I say
"trust the police and the law."

00:13:25.639 --> 00:13:27.620
How often have I cleaned up your mess?

00:13:28.279 --> 00:13:31.220
But if we wait for you,
it could take months.

00:13:31.399 --> 00:13:34.200
The construction crew
needs the money to eat.

00:13:34.460 --> 00:13:37.279
So you threatened that guy with hammers?

00:13:40.220 --> 00:13:42.620
He's a scammer who cheated you.

00:13:44.460 --> 00:13:46.080
But what you did was worse.

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:47.720
You broke the law, understand?

00:13:51.879 --> 00:13:55.379
Zhu, I'll repay that money soon.

00:13:56.740 --> 00:14:00.340
Is it about money?
You're like my own brother.

00:14:00.340 --> 00:14:00.960
You...

00:14:01.200 --> 00:14:03.460
I fear that if you
keep acting recklessly,

00:14:03.639 --> 00:14:06.259
you'll do something truly irreversible.

00:14:06.259 --> 00:14:08.080
We're driven to this by those bosses.

00:14:17.899 --> 00:14:21.740
Wait, Zhu, you used
your paycheck for my debt.

00:14:22.019 --> 00:14:23.460
How will you explain this at home?

00:14:23.879 --> 00:14:25.740
I run my household. Don't worry.

00:14:51.460 --> 00:14:52.120
You're back?

00:14:56.519 --> 00:14:57.700
No overtime today?

00:14:58.500 --> 00:15:00.960
Just rest and take care of our baby.

00:15:01.759 --> 00:15:03.759
Who told you to cook?

00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:06.100
How did you know?

00:15:07.259 --> 00:15:08.480
I just thought

00:15:09.019 --> 00:15:11.580
it's been three months.
I'm not that fragile.

00:15:12.100 --> 00:15:13.120
I'll cook dinner.

00:15:13.399 --> 00:15:15.220
Okay. Why are you home so early?

00:15:15.639 --> 00:15:18.860
Something came up.
I took leave from the station.

00:15:26.080 --> 00:15:26.600
Huifen.

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:31.840
What is it?

00:15:32.139 --> 00:15:33.259
I need to confess something.

00:15:34.220 --> 00:15:37.460
I did something
violating family discipline.

00:15:43.340 --> 00:15:44.200
Speak.

00:15:45.379 --> 00:15:46.279
Who's that woman?

00:15:49.879 --> 00:15:50.440
No.

00:15:52.399 --> 00:15:54.460
It's my buddy Meng Guangcai.

00:15:56.100 --> 00:15:58.500
He got scammed
and can't repay the money.

00:15:59.399 --> 00:16:02.200
So I... I guaranteed his debt.

00:16:02.620 --> 00:16:03.360
How much?

00:16:03.720 --> 00:16:04.460
2,500.

00:16:04.460 --> 00:16:05.720
2,500?

00:16:06.460 --> 00:16:09.879
I lent him my paycheck today too
to cover the debt.

00:16:10.460 --> 00:16:11.879
Huifen, please don't be angry.

00:16:15.639 --> 00:16:17.019
What were you thinking, Zhu Helai?

00:16:18.379 --> 00:16:20.840
How could I be angry? Lend it.

00:16:23.259 --> 00:16:25.220
You two aren't just acquaintances.

00:16:26.379 --> 00:16:28.220
He's always been proud.

00:16:29.100 --> 00:16:33.220
If he asked you, he must be desperate.

00:16:33.860 --> 00:16:37.200
If you won't help your sworn brother,
who will?

00:16:38.139 --> 00:16:40.279
You're incredible.

00:16:40.279 --> 00:16:43.840
You've got no family in Beiyan.

00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:45.840
That makes him family.

00:16:47.379 --> 00:16:50.879
Lend it. We've got to help him.
We'll make do.

00:16:52.779 --> 00:16:55.639
I've got my salary.
I'll cover expenses this month.

00:16:56.899 --> 00:16:58.139
See? This is...

00:16:58.139 --> 00:16:59.620
What? What are you doing?

00:16:59.620 --> 00:17:01.019
You're my wife. What's wrong?

00:17:01.620 --> 00:17:02.720
So annoying.

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:32.579
Look at you. You're pregnant
but still working so many shifts.

00:17:32.839 --> 00:17:34.700
You work much harder than before.

00:17:35.640 --> 00:17:37.420
My due date's still far off.

00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:39.819
I figured I'd work more
while I still can.

00:17:40.579 --> 00:17:41.740
Okay, how many do you want?

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:42.759
I'll take four.

00:17:42.759 --> 00:17:44.299
Okay, noted for you, Ms. Yin.

00:17:44.299 --> 00:17:44.940
Thanks.

00:18:07.482 --> 00:18:12.794
(Beiyan County Hospital)

00:18:14.079 --> 00:18:16.400
The doctor said
it was caused by overwork.

00:18:17.160 --> 00:18:19.539
I told you not to work overtime so much.

00:18:19.940 --> 00:18:21.420
Why wouldn't you listen?

00:18:29.640 --> 00:18:32.980
It's not about losing the baby.

00:18:33.059 --> 00:18:34.559
I'm worried about your health.

00:18:37.180 --> 00:18:37.940
I just...

00:18:39.980 --> 00:18:41.579
I just wanted to get the bonus

00:18:42.779 --> 00:18:44.339
at month-end.

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:02.299
Okay. Thanks.

00:19:03.640 --> 00:19:06.539
Laoda, what's the occasion today?

00:19:06.539 --> 00:19:07.680
Treating me to oat noodles?

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:08.779
Nothing special.

00:19:09.460 --> 00:19:10.980
I haven't seen you in a long time.

00:19:11.680 --> 00:19:15.259
You vanish after work every day,
no idea where you go.

00:19:16.019 --> 00:19:19.019
It's family stuff.
I need to go home early.

00:19:19.019 --> 00:19:20.339
What family stuff? So important?

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:22.779
You know what it is, don't you?

00:19:27.400 --> 00:19:29.740
When did I last see your wife?

00:19:30.319 --> 00:19:32.779
She was craving spicy food back then.

00:19:32.779 --> 00:19:35.220
I said then, it must be a girl.

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:36.920
Due soon?

00:19:37.920 --> 00:19:38.680
One month to go.

00:19:39.079 --> 00:19:39.940
Name picked out?

00:19:40.140 --> 00:19:44.220
My wife wants a repeated character
in the name, like Qianqian.

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:45.259
Qianqian?

00:19:45.839 --> 00:19:49.056
Qianqian. Lin Qianqian.
Nice name. Very nice.

00:19:49.056 --> 00:19:50.079
- Nice name.
- Really?

00:19:50.079 --> 00:19:51.640
Pleasant to hear and easy to remember.

00:19:51.940 --> 00:19:54.000
But, Laosan, I have to criticize you.

00:19:54.440 --> 00:19:57.319
Such a big, wonderful thing,
and you didn't tell us.

00:19:59.960 --> 00:20:00.980
Afraid I'd be upset?

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:03.680
Laoda,

00:20:05.180 --> 00:20:07.819
we were all really sad
about what happened to you.

00:20:08.039 --> 00:20:09.319
We didn't know how to help.

00:20:11.180 --> 00:20:13.920
From now on,
my daughter is your daughter.

00:20:13.920 --> 00:20:15.960
Treat her like your own daughter, okay?

00:20:16.299 --> 00:20:17.539
Absolutely.

00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:22.559
Listen, if Huifen and I
ever have a son later,

00:20:23.019 --> 00:20:24.140
we must become in-laws.

00:20:24.140 --> 00:20:24.900
Absolutely.

00:20:27.680 --> 00:20:29.640
Seeing you like this now
puts my mind at ease.

00:20:33.640 --> 00:20:34.559
How is your wife?

00:20:36.339 --> 00:20:39.180
The miscarriage drained her vitality.

00:20:39.819 --> 00:20:41.019
Her health hasn't been great.

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:44.980
She has to
go to the hospital frequently.

00:20:45.279 --> 00:20:48.640
She needs proper rest.
No lasting issues.

00:20:50.440 --> 00:20:53.660
I asked you to eat today

00:20:54.440 --> 00:20:55.819
also because of that.

00:20:57.039 --> 00:20:59.220
I felt like you were
beating around the bush today.

00:20:59.220 --> 00:20:59.940
What is it?

00:21:05.420 --> 00:21:06.140
- No.
- Just say it.

00:21:08.319 --> 00:21:09.440
It's hard to bring up.

00:21:09.640 --> 00:21:10.940
Just tell me.

00:21:11.059 --> 00:21:12.680
If this were an interrogation,

00:21:12.680 --> 00:21:15.680
I wouldn't even know
what it's about or what to confess.

00:21:16.140 --> 00:21:19.299
I'm a bit short on cash lately.

00:21:20.200 --> 00:21:23.440
I want to find a good doctor
to help Huifen recuperate.

00:21:24.799 --> 00:21:26.940
I'd like to borrow 200 yuan from you.

00:21:33.299 --> 00:21:36.319
But you've got your baby coming soon.
You're not flush, either.

00:21:36.799 --> 00:21:38.539
Sorry. I shouldn't have asked.

00:21:39.039 --> 00:21:40.339
Just forget I said anything.

00:21:40.700 --> 00:21:42.779
You're overthinking it.
I was just thinking

00:21:42.779 --> 00:21:45.039
how much is left in my passbook.

00:21:48.500 --> 00:21:51.579
Okay, our family financial policy
is more liberal than yours. No problem.

00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:55.720
Laosan, if you have some spare,

00:21:56.299 --> 00:21:57.539
just help me out temporarily.

00:21:57.539 --> 00:22:00.579
Isn't it due in a month?
I'll pay you back before the baby comes.

00:22:01.400 --> 00:22:04.259
This little thing
had you all bottled up?

00:22:05.539 --> 00:22:07.799
I happen to have the passbook
with me today.

00:22:08.299 --> 00:22:10.519
I'll go get the cash now.
The credit union's next door.

00:22:11.339 --> 00:22:12.740
You eat and wait for me.

00:22:14.906 --> 00:22:16.698
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)

00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:22.980
Police!

00:22:42.140 --> 00:22:43.079
Help!

00:22:43.779 --> 00:22:45.240
Let me out!

00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:47.319
Help!

00:23:02.362 --> 00:23:06.336
(Police Badge)

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:19.720
Lin Shan?

00:23:20.220 --> 00:23:21.000
Hurry!

00:23:21.180 --> 00:23:21.900
Hurry!

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:23.779
Lin Shan!

00:23:26.420 --> 00:23:27.200
Lin Shan!

00:23:30.400 --> 00:23:31.400
Hold on!

00:23:35.640 --> 00:23:36.200
Master?

00:23:36.680 --> 00:23:37.319
It's my master.

00:23:37.559 --> 00:23:39.559
- Quanyi.
- Am I right? Is that my master?

00:23:39.559 --> 00:23:40.759
It's him. Quanyi, listen.

00:23:40.759 --> 00:23:41.559
Why is he here?

00:23:41.720 --> 00:23:42.480
Focus on the job.

00:23:42.480 --> 00:23:44.299
- Master!
- Quanyi! Quanyi!

00:23:44.339 --> 00:23:45.019
Master!

00:23:45.019 --> 00:23:45.799
- Let me see him.
- Quanyi!

00:23:45.799 --> 00:23:47.519
Listen to me. Listen.

00:23:47.519 --> 00:23:48.279
I'm here.

00:23:48.279 --> 00:23:50.019
- I'm here. I'm here.
- Why is he here?

00:23:50.039 --> 00:23:51.140
Focus on your job now.

00:23:51.220 --> 00:23:51.920
Go.

00:23:59.700 --> 00:24:01.680
(Public Phone)
Liu Jingjing, phone call.

00:24:03.079 --> 00:24:03.759
Who is it?

00:24:04.059 --> 00:24:06.579
It's the police, asking for you.

00:24:07.519 --> 00:24:09.539
Hello? Yes, speaking.

00:24:12.299 --> 00:24:13.019
What?

00:24:15.539 --> 00:24:16.220
Okay.

00:24:17.920 --> 00:24:19.039
I'll come right away.

00:24:21.220 --> 00:24:21.839
Jingjing!

00:24:22.400 --> 00:24:23.500
My belly...

00:24:23.500 --> 00:24:24.259
Jingjing!

00:24:24.319 --> 00:24:25.299
What's happening?

00:24:25.779 --> 00:24:26.819
Get a doctor.

00:24:27.019 --> 00:24:27.680
What's wrong?

00:24:29.850 --> 00:24:33.632
(Quiet)

00:24:35.259 --> 00:24:36.039
It's all my fault.

00:24:38.460 --> 00:24:39.079
Helai,

00:24:40.299 --> 00:24:43.279
the doctor said that Lin Shan
passed the most critical stage.

00:24:43.279 --> 00:24:45.039
He will definitely pull through.

00:24:45.299 --> 00:24:46.440
It's all my fault.

00:24:49.319 --> 00:24:50.259
It's all my fault.

00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:51.799
Keep steady, will you?

00:24:52.299 --> 00:24:53.420
It's all my fault.

00:24:55.740 --> 00:24:56.640
It's all my fault.

00:24:57.319 --> 00:24:58.799
Who is Liu Jingjing's family?

00:24:58.799 --> 00:24:59.920
All three of us are.

00:24:59.920 --> 00:25:01.059
Doctor, how is she doing?

00:25:01.059 --> 00:25:04.759
The mother was in shock.
Premature birth caused severe bleeding.

00:25:04.759 --> 00:25:08.000
The mother's life is at risk.
You need to mentally prepare yourselves.

00:25:08.000 --> 00:25:09.920
We will do our utmost to save her.

00:25:10.180 --> 00:25:11.839
Please, doctor.

00:25:12.079 --> 00:25:13.259
Think of something, doctor.

00:25:22.039 --> 00:25:23.259
Who told Liu Jingjing?

00:25:24.319 --> 00:25:25.339
Shouldn't it be a secret?

00:25:28.980 --> 00:25:30.460
After Lin Shan got hurt,

00:25:31.640 --> 00:25:33.579
our colleagues called his wife.

00:25:34.299 --> 00:25:35.740
She's far along in her pregnancy.

00:25:35.740 --> 00:25:37.420
Such a shock would indeed...

00:25:40.440 --> 00:25:41.200
What do you mean?

00:25:43.839 --> 00:25:45.299
So the whole family might be gone?

00:26:05.018 --> 00:26:08.180
(Police)

00:26:08.180 --> 00:26:09.759
Tell us everything you saw.

00:26:10.240 --> 00:26:12.960
It was three men.
I remember that clearly.

00:26:13.579 --> 00:26:15.700
They came in with guns,
trying to smash our glass.

00:26:15.700 --> 00:26:18.740
At first, three men charged in.

00:26:19.440 --> 00:26:21.440
The security guard
got into a fight with them.

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:23.240
But he couldn't beat them.

00:26:24.700 --> 00:26:26.700
Then we were locked up.

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:27.400
(Deposit Voluntarily, Withdraw Freely)

00:26:27.400 --> 00:26:28.220
(Later,)

00:26:28.220 --> 00:26:28.759
Don't move!

00:26:29.160 --> 00:26:30.720
(I heard a police officer arrive.)

00:26:31.480 --> 00:26:32.339
Then later,

00:26:32.640 --> 00:26:34.180
I heard a gunshot.

00:26:36.799 --> 00:26:37.460
Knife.

00:26:42.799 --> 00:26:45.200
Knife. Knife. Knife.

00:26:45.200 --> 00:26:47.039
They all wore hoods.
I couldn't see anything.

00:26:47.420 --> 00:26:49.299
(I was in the break room
during the robbery.)

00:26:49.839 --> 00:26:52.319
(I hadn't seen the robbers yet
when they were forced in.)

00:26:52.819 --> 00:26:55.799
According to He Lili,
there should have been three of them.

00:26:57.299 --> 00:26:58.019
Next.

00:27:01.559 --> 00:27:02.259
Captain Liu.

00:27:02.980 --> 00:27:03.539
Zhu.

00:27:03.799 --> 00:27:04.460
Guangcai.

00:27:05.839 --> 00:27:07.240
Guangcai, do you work here?

00:27:08.579 --> 00:27:09.940
I just started not long ago.

00:27:12.740 --> 00:27:14.960
Zhu, what's going on? Such a big deal.

00:27:15.079 --> 00:27:18.240
It's nothing,
just some routine questioning.

00:27:18.980 --> 00:27:20.299
Answer what's asked, okay?

00:27:20.799 --> 00:27:22.200
Where were you on June 10th?

00:27:23.980 --> 00:27:25.480
June 10th?

00:27:26.500 --> 00:27:28.240
On the 10th, I was in Jinwan.

00:27:29.079 --> 00:27:30.319
Why did you go to Jinwan?

00:27:31.160 --> 00:27:35.640
Zhu knows. I take over ten people
to work at construction sites.

00:27:35.640 --> 00:27:38.839
A couple days ago, I heard
a job in Jinwan urgently needed workers.

00:27:39.039 --> 00:27:43.059
And the pay was good.
So I got excited and rushed over.

00:27:45.400 --> 00:27:46.440
The day before yesterday.

00:27:48.500 --> 00:27:49.839
You came back so quickly?

00:27:50.140 --> 00:27:52.079
That job was popular.
Lots of people wanted it.

00:27:52.519 --> 00:27:53.539
We didn't get it.

00:27:54.539 --> 00:27:56.500
We took the train back
the very next day.

00:27:56.680 --> 00:27:59.660
Wasted money on those train tickets.

00:28:00.319 --> 00:28:01.539
Do you still have your ticket?

00:28:03.460 --> 00:28:04.839
I haven't washed my clothes.

00:28:05.299 --> 00:28:08.539
The ticket should be in my pocket.
Let me go look for it.

00:28:08.539 --> 00:28:10.460
Alright, please go get it.

00:28:10.460 --> 00:28:11.700
We'll verify it, okay?

00:28:13.299 --> 00:28:15.900
Guangcai, is everything okay?

00:28:17.160 --> 00:28:17.980
Of course.

00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:20.920
I... I just thought you looked unwell.

00:28:21.960 --> 00:28:23.339
You people need to rest well.

00:28:24.839 --> 00:28:26.019
Alright, go get the ticket.

00:28:26.220 --> 00:28:26.940
Okay.

00:28:44.634 --> 00:28:46.980
(Transcript, Train Ticket)

00:28:46.980 --> 00:28:48.079
Any issue with the ticket?

00:28:49.160 --> 00:28:49.940
No.

00:28:50.779 --> 00:28:52.539
Just thinking about something.

00:28:53.019 --> 00:28:53.940
Not even eating?

00:28:54.740 --> 00:28:55.539
Got you some food.

00:28:59.819 --> 00:29:01.160
Food keeps you going.

00:29:03.079 --> 00:29:04.539
Miss one meal, and you're starving.

00:29:07.799 --> 00:29:09.180
Don't overthink things.

00:29:09.920 --> 00:29:12.839
We'll catch those scoundrels
and give Lin Shan justice.

00:29:15.259 --> 00:29:17.400
That gang's luck is just too good.

00:29:18.799 --> 00:29:20.799
From them entering the credit union
to leaving,

00:29:21.500 --> 00:29:25.299
besides Laosan, almost no one
witnessed any useful information.

00:29:26.039 --> 00:29:27.960
One witness
even got scared out of his mind.

00:29:29.940 --> 00:29:32.200
After canvassing, six or seven citizens

00:29:32.539 --> 00:29:34.259
said they might have seen them.

00:29:34.680 --> 00:29:38.019
Others were completely uncertain.

00:29:38.799 --> 00:29:40.799
These past few years,
with the economy opening up,

00:29:41.740 --> 00:29:45.259
there's a lot of migrant population.
And our investigation scope is huge.

00:29:45.920 --> 00:29:47.180
It's quite difficult.

00:29:47.700 --> 00:29:49.680
The scene did leave us some things.

00:29:49.940 --> 00:29:52.192
Besides Lin Shan's,
there were two other blood stains.

00:29:52.460 --> 00:29:54.779
One was verified to be
from the security guard.

00:29:55.940 --> 00:29:59.500
The other was very likely
from one of the robbers.

00:30:02.819 --> 00:30:04.240
(Outpatient of Beiyan County Hospital)
We work in three shifts.

00:30:04.480 --> 00:30:08.160
I haven't heard about any gunshot wounds
or suspected gunshot wounds.

00:30:08.559 --> 00:30:12.680
If there were, we'd definitely
report it to you immediately.

00:30:13.220 --> 00:30:16.079
Please pull all external injury records
from June 10.

00:30:17.140 --> 00:30:18.259
Let me check for you.

00:30:18.259 --> 00:30:29.319
(Outpatient of Beiyan County Hospital)

00:30:29.319 --> 00:30:30.059
Zhu?

00:30:32.539 --> 00:30:33.299
Guangcai?

00:30:35.980 --> 00:30:37.299
Have you tried these cigarettes?

00:30:37.299 --> 00:30:39.680
No, thanks.
My throat's been bothering me.

00:30:40.019 --> 00:30:41.799
Too much going on. I'm swamped.

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:45.140
You knew I was here?
You were waiting for me?

00:30:45.519 --> 00:30:47.039
No, I just happened to run into you.

00:30:47.220 --> 00:30:48.180
Then why are you here?

00:30:48.940 --> 00:30:50.700
Xiaoliang's health is pretty poor.

00:30:50.700 --> 00:30:53.079
I came to get some medicine
from his doctor.

00:30:53.660 --> 00:30:57.099
These cigarettes were meant for him.
What a coincidence running into you.

00:30:59.039 --> 00:30:59.779
Zhu,

00:31:00.672 --> 00:31:02.304
everyone on the site
is talking about it.

00:31:02.740 --> 00:31:03.559
About what?

00:31:09.539 --> 00:31:11.180
That robbery case.

00:31:12.680 --> 00:31:14.539
The way you asked that
kind of threw me off.

00:31:15.259 --> 00:31:16.920
Is the robbery case that hard to solve?

00:31:17.720 --> 00:31:19.680
Do you have any suspects?

00:31:21.440 --> 00:31:22.539
Why do you care?

00:31:23.700 --> 00:31:25.839
I don't care about the case itself.

00:31:26.500 --> 00:31:29.799
It's just that last time I saw you,
you didn't look so good.

00:31:30.299 --> 00:31:32.200
I'm unsure how long
you'll be investigating.

00:31:32.940 --> 00:31:34.579
You really need
to take care of yourself.

00:31:37.700 --> 00:31:38.940
In that case,

00:31:39.259 --> 00:31:42.460
one of my cop buddies
got shot and injured.

00:31:42.779 --> 00:31:44.759
He's lying in the hospital.
Still there now.

00:31:45.180 --> 00:31:46.180
But rest assured.

00:31:46.640 --> 00:31:49.799
No matter what.
I will track those guys down.

00:31:52.299 --> 00:31:53.079
Guangcai.

00:31:57.319 --> 00:31:58.440
You're acting strange today.

00:31:59.500 --> 00:32:01.039
You're hiding something.

00:32:04.039 --> 00:32:05.819
No wonder we're like brothers.

00:32:06.299 --> 00:32:07.559
I can't hide anything from you.

00:32:08.680 --> 00:32:09.660
Here's the thing.

00:32:10.180 --> 00:32:12.759
I'm planning to go out and find work.

00:32:13.259 --> 00:32:14.019
Where to?

00:32:14.180 --> 00:32:15.039
To Guangnan.

00:32:15.980 --> 00:32:16.839
So sudden?

00:32:18.240 --> 00:32:19.936
I've been thinking about it for a while.

00:32:21.079 --> 00:32:24.519
Beiyan's great and all,
but the pay is just too low.

00:32:25.400 --> 00:32:27.480
I've worked on so many sites,

00:32:27.700 --> 00:32:29.240
but I just can't save money.

00:32:30.299 --> 00:32:31.640
Xiaoliang's health isn't great.

00:32:32.220 --> 00:32:33.740
I need to start preparing ahead.

00:32:34.500 --> 00:32:35.539
That's the right thought.

00:32:36.039 --> 00:32:37.140
Go out and earn some money.

00:32:37.700 --> 00:32:39.900
Travel with extra cash.
Let me see if I have some cash.

00:32:39.900 --> 00:32:41.039
No, Zhu, I don't need it.

00:32:41.539 --> 00:32:42.680
No need. I have some.

00:32:42.920 --> 00:32:45.180
A workmate hooked me up.
They provide meals as I arrive.

00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:49.240
I'd like to have a meal with you
before I leave, Zhu.

00:32:49.240 --> 00:32:50.220
Come on.

00:32:51.039 --> 00:32:53.259
I'm crazy busy every day.
No time for meals.

00:32:53.640 --> 00:32:56.299
Guangcai, bye.
I need to get back to work.

00:32:57.079 --> 00:32:59.440
Take good care of yourself out there.

00:32:59.440 --> 00:33:00.039
I know.

00:33:00.559 --> 00:33:02.980
Actually, I'm following your advice

00:33:03.480 --> 00:33:05.660
to go out and make something of myself.

00:33:07.579 --> 00:33:08.299
Take care.

00:33:09.759 --> 00:33:10.440
I'm heading off.

00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:11.539
Zhu.

00:33:29.242 --> 00:33:32.896
(Demonstration Room)

00:33:36.000 --> 00:33:37.799
I didn't stop him
from joining the task force.

00:33:42.420 --> 00:33:45.259
Don't you know what condition he has?

00:33:46.180 --> 00:33:46.920
We know.

00:33:47.539 --> 00:33:50.000
Car crash. Interrogation.

00:33:51.339 --> 00:33:52.539
With his health like that,

00:33:54.299 --> 00:33:55.539
could he possibly handle it?

00:34:01.980 --> 00:34:02.740
Huifen,

00:34:04.440 --> 00:34:05.400
don't be upset.

00:34:10.840 --> 00:34:12.139
It's my fault.

00:34:13.079 --> 00:34:16.079
Mrs. Zhu, this whole thing is my fault.

00:34:16.400 --> 00:34:17.639
I didn't watch him closely.

00:34:18.320 --> 00:34:20.920
From now on, whoever wants
to watch him can do it. I can't.

00:34:21.079 --> 00:34:24.559
He's yours now. This family doesn't
want him anymore. He lied to me.

00:34:26.699 --> 00:34:28.000
He doesn't take meds on time.

00:34:30.360 --> 00:34:33.480
Tell me, can he even
live properly like this?

00:34:35.400 --> 00:34:37.420
Don't think the worst about everything.

00:34:42.159 --> 00:34:44.340
Mom, Dad's awake.

00:34:48.440 --> 00:34:49.420
Zhu, you're awake?

00:34:50.780 --> 00:34:51.639
Are you lucid?

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.039
Master.

00:34:53.440 --> 00:34:54.340
Zhu, are you okay?

00:34:54.860 --> 00:34:55.500
I'm fine.

00:34:55.940 --> 00:34:58.179
Doctor's here for rounds.
Please make way.

00:34:58.659 --> 00:34:59.760
Doctor, he's awake.

00:35:00.288 --> 00:35:01.119
Please take a look.

00:35:01.119 --> 00:35:02.880
Bed 13, Zhu Helai, right?

00:35:04.119 --> 00:35:06.480
How are you feeling? Any better?

00:35:06.760 --> 00:35:07.679
Much better.

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:11.139
Doctor, what's wrong with him?

00:35:11.139 --> 00:35:16.099
It's hypoglycemia from overexertion.
He absolutely must rest.

00:35:17.579 --> 00:35:19.519
He had a stroke before, correct?

00:35:20.199 --> 00:35:21.019
Back in 2006.

00:35:21.460 --> 00:35:22.920
He needs rest even more.

00:35:23.340 --> 00:35:25.139
He needs to keep his emotions stable.

00:35:25.440 --> 00:35:26.980
No prolonged fatigue.

00:35:28.300 --> 00:35:28.840
Okay.

00:35:29.619 --> 00:35:31.119
We'll do a brain CT scan tomorrow.

00:35:31.880 --> 00:35:32.619
Thanks, doctor.

00:35:32.619 --> 00:35:33.719
- Thanks.
- You're welcome.

00:35:39.860 --> 00:35:41.380
Look at the state he's in now.

00:35:43.300 --> 00:35:44.099
Chief Liu,

00:35:46.699 --> 00:35:49.840
you two went
to the police academy together.

00:35:50.139 --> 00:35:51.760
You keep climbing higher and higher.

00:35:52.159 --> 00:35:55.059
But my husband
is stuck cooking in Logistics.

00:35:56.260 --> 00:35:57.980
We've never asked you
for a favor, have we?

00:35:57.980 --> 00:36:00.380
Enough, why are you picking on him?

00:36:00.599 --> 00:36:02.920
Dad, Mom just cares about you.

00:36:10.900 --> 00:36:15.119
Zhu, I know you've wanted
to solve this case for years.

00:36:15.380 --> 00:36:17.059
It has been eating at you.

00:36:17.519 --> 00:36:19.460
Qianqian and I never stopped you
all these years.

00:36:19.880 --> 00:36:22.099
But now you're pushing yourself
to death, you know?

00:36:23.559 --> 00:36:25.980
The case is making progress now, okay?

00:36:25.980 --> 00:36:28.000
Are you the only cop in the world?

00:36:28.000 --> 00:36:29.579
Master, don't argue back.

00:36:30.420 --> 00:36:33.579
Just rest well in the hospital.
Mrs. Zhu is just worried about you.

00:36:33.840 --> 00:36:35.619
The main task now is to seize the chance

00:36:36.280 --> 00:36:40.380
with Wang Dazhu here
and get his confession in one go.

00:36:40.480 --> 00:36:41.840
- Enough.
- Dad.

00:36:42.159 --> 00:36:43.139
Shut up.

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:47.900
You think you're still young?
Don't you know your age?

00:36:47.900 --> 00:36:50.460
That was the main street
of the pedestrian zone.

00:36:50.940 --> 00:36:51.980
That place was packed.

00:36:52.659 --> 00:36:55.519
What if Wang Dazhu got desperate
and charged into the crowd?

00:36:55.679 --> 00:36:56.679
Can you handle that?

00:36:56.679 --> 00:36:58.679
Laoer, I know what you're thinking.

00:36:59.280 --> 00:37:01.380
You see me stuck here and can't get out.

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:03.400
You want me replaced, right?

00:37:03.400 --> 00:37:04.619
Enough. Replaced by whom?

00:37:04.699 --> 00:37:05.539
I know him best.

00:37:05.539 --> 00:37:07.300
Lie here properly for five days.

00:37:07.300 --> 00:37:08.679
He's as stubborn as an oak.

00:37:08.679 --> 00:37:10.039
Alright, stop talking.

00:37:10.280 --> 00:37:11.519
I can push through

00:37:11.519 --> 00:37:12.760
and get his confession.

00:37:12.760 --> 00:37:13.539
- Do you believe me?
- Watch him.

00:37:13.539 --> 00:37:14.380
Five days.

00:37:14.619 --> 00:37:15.139
Yes.

00:37:15.179 --> 00:37:16.860
Or you'll be writing
a self-criticism too.

00:37:18.539 --> 00:37:21.199
Master, just rest easy here.

00:37:21.659 --> 00:37:24.320
If anything happens to Wang Dazhu,
I'll report to you immediately.

00:37:27.099 --> 00:37:29.280
Who's the team leader, you or him?
Why report to him?

00:37:29.519 --> 00:37:30.440
He is the team leader,

00:37:30.440 --> 00:37:31.519
but I'm his master.

00:37:31.519 --> 00:37:32.340
Fine.

00:37:32.340 --> 00:37:33.059
He has to...

00:37:33.059 --> 00:37:34.340
Alright, stop talking.

00:37:34.659 --> 00:37:35.760
What are you all doing?

00:37:35.960 --> 00:37:37.579
Why are you arguing in the ward?

00:37:38.179 --> 00:37:39.059
I'm so sorry.

00:37:40.159 --> 00:37:40.960
Sorry.

00:37:42.042 --> 00:37:45.280
(Police)

00:37:48.920 --> 00:37:51.880
Wang Dazhu has more tricks
than Meng Guangcai.

00:37:52.380 --> 00:37:55.659
We've been interrogating him,
and he keeps playing dumb.

00:37:55.960 --> 00:37:58.420
I asked him
why he drove through the barrier.

00:37:58.420 --> 00:38:01.079
He said he didn't know how to drive
and accidentally hit the gas.

00:38:01.199 --> 00:38:03.000
Beyond that, he refuses to say anything.

00:38:03.199 --> 00:38:06.079
We told him to write a statement,
and he dragged it out word by word.

00:38:06.079 --> 00:38:08.119
He claims he can't write
and needs a dictionary.

00:38:09.380 --> 00:38:13.360
Where did Officer Zhu get the idea
he's definitely involved in this case?

00:38:13.539 --> 00:38:16.880
Now he insists the crash happened
because Officer Zhu scared him.

00:38:16.880 --> 00:38:20.019
At most, we can charge him
with reckless driving and fleeing.

00:38:20.340 --> 00:38:22.360
He hasn't handled a case in so long

00:38:22.920 --> 00:38:25.780
and is still stuck in the old routine
of bringing them in first.

00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:29.472
He ignores real suspects
and causes trouble for the task force.

00:38:30.528 --> 00:38:32.300
We can't just let him go, can we?

00:38:33.119 --> 00:38:34.000
No, we can't.

00:38:34.579 --> 00:38:36.460
Reckless driving alone means detention.

00:38:36.460 --> 00:38:38.380
Besides, he's a friend of Meng Guangcai.

00:38:38.980 --> 00:38:41.900
Since he's here, we have to squeeze
something useful out of him.

00:38:42.336 --> 00:38:43.119
Ask him if he knows

00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:45.960
the relationship between
Meng Guangcai, Zuo Long, and Ma Zhongwu.

00:38:46.019 --> 00:38:46.752
Yes.

00:38:53.306 --> 00:38:56.122
(Beiyan Central Hospital)

00:38:59.019 --> 00:39:03.719
(I'm a bit short on cash lately.
I'd like to borrow 200 yuan from you.)

00:39:06.619 --> 00:39:08.820
(I happen to have the passbook
with me today.)

00:39:09.920 --> 00:39:12.420
(I'll go get the cash now.
The credit union's next door.)

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:10.340
Li Quanyi.

00:40:10.340 --> 00:40:11.599
Don't call me.

00:40:14.260 --> 00:40:16.360
I'm responsible
for what happened to your master.

00:40:16.360 --> 00:40:17.920
Don't give me that.

00:40:21.139 --> 00:40:22.860
I know you've resented me all along.

00:40:26.500 --> 00:40:27.500
Resent you?

00:40:28.519 --> 00:40:29.800
Why would I resent you?

00:40:30.079 --> 00:40:30.960
I don't resent you.

00:40:33.380 --> 00:40:35.000
I feel sorry for my master.

00:40:38.840 --> 00:40:40.000
Back then,

00:40:40.559 --> 00:40:43.460
his investigative skills
were unmatched in the police station.

00:40:43.980 --> 00:40:47.079
As such a promising officer,
why did he just collapse like that?

00:40:48.500 --> 00:40:50.280
Why did you send him
to the credit union?

00:40:50.599 --> 00:40:52.500
Why did you make him go?

00:40:55.260 --> 00:40:57.000
He was like an older brother to me.

00:40:58.800 --> 00:41:00.280
Back then, he took me on calls.

00:41:01.099 --> 00:41:03.199
He always stood in front, protecting me.

00:41:09.320 --> 00:41:10.599
He's such a good man.

00:41:12.579 --> 00:41:14.699
Why has he been lying there
for 18 years?

00:41:15.420 --> 00:41:17.059
How could he lie there for 18 years?

00:41:17.059 --> 00:41:18.420
It shouldn't have been him.

00:41:22.119 --> 00:41:25.940
(The person who stood in front
to protect me was gone.)

00:41:27.119 --> 00:41:29.079
How I wish my master would wake up.

00:41:30.940 --> 00:41:33.059
I want to chat with him
and keep him company.

00:41:33.559 --> 00:41:35.159
Even one look from him would be enough.

00:41:38.519 --> 00:41:39.599
I want to tell him,

00:41:41.679 --> 00:41:43.099
"Your disciple now has the ability

00:41:46.500 --> 00:41:48.900
to stand in front of you
and protect you."

00:41:55.179 --> 00:41:58.400
So, what have you found out
after all these years?

00:41:59.300 --> 00:42:00.119
Listen to me.

00:42:01.099 --> 00:42:03.980
I don't want to see
you messing up the task force.

00:42:05.000 --> 00:42:06.940
I will personally close this case

00:42:09.539 --> 00:42:10.900
and give my master justice.

00:42:54.940 --> 00:42:55.800
Zhu,

00:42:58.599 --> 00:42:59.659
you like cars too?

00:43:00.099 --> 00:43:00.760
Just looking.

00:43:01.619 --> 00:43:03.920
Zhu, I heard about your hospitalization.

00:43:04.380 --> 00:43:05.699
I'd been wanting to visit.

00:43:05.699 --> 00:43:08.099
But the company lacked staff.

00:43:08.440 --> 00:43:09.519
I didn't have the chance.

00:43:10.880 --> 00:43:12.860
It's been so many years, Lijun.

00:43:13.780 --> 00:43:16.960
You and Wang Dazhu
have both become big bosses.

00:43:16.960 --> 00:43:17.820
Look at this car.

00:43:18.139 --> 00:43:20.019
Unlike me, still just a small-time cop.

00:43:20.019 --> 00:43:22.639
Someone as insignificant
as me got hospitalized,

00:43:22.820 --> 00:43:25.280
and you, Lijun,
knew about it immediately?

00:43:27.599 --> 00:43:29.420
You're keeping tabs on us all the time.

00:43:29.760 --> 00:43:31.659
We care about you every single moment.

00:43:32.099 --> 00:43:33.360
We both know that.

00:43:34.340 --> 00:43:35.340
Know what?

00:43:38.179 --> 00:43:41.019
I have the confidence
to communicate openly with the police.

00:43:41.639 --> 00:43:42.360
Zhu.

00:43:42.980 --> 00:43:44.860
Just give me a call
if you have questions.

00:43:44.860 --> 00:43:45.820
I'll report anytime.

00:43:46.199 --> 00:43:48.099
No need to watch me so intently.

00:43:50.079 --> 00:43:54.340
You're a smart guy after all,
unlike Wang Dazhu.

00:43:56.440 --> 00:43:58.820
Why are you so sure I'm watching you

00:43:59.659 --> 00:44:01.179
and not someone else?

00:44:18.618 --> 00:44:19.199
(Li Fen, Caisheng Group Executive)

00:44:19.199 --> 00:44:19.980
Uncle.

00:44:20.940 --> 00:44:23.300
The Meng Guangcai matter
might not be so simple.

00:44:23.679 --> 00:44:24.960
We need to be prepared.

00:44:25.980 --> 00:44:28.000
Meet tomorrow morning at the usual spot.

00:44:38.180 --> 00:44:43.204
=The Silent Rift=